&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting new role has become available for an experienced Associate Practitioner in Musgrove Park Hospital&#39;s Endoscopy unit. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants need to have a foundation degree or diploma in a health care related subject, ideally they will have experience of working within the endoscopy setting as well as experience of providing direct patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should be used to working in a busy environment, be self motivated and be a great team player.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There may be a requirement to take part in the on call rota for the department&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Elizabeth Herbison, Senior Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;elizabeth.herbison@SomersetFT.nhs.uk, 01823 343806&lt;/p&gt;
